{
  "text": "In that case, we better ask you only one question, unless you deem it all right to ask any more questions than that. The one question of bothering us, which I got in meditation, may be an inappropriate question, but I feel it my duty to ask it because it is central to the instrument's mental condition and ours. Having to do with the two cats which we were going to take to have worked upon today for teeth cleaning and the small growth removed from Gandalf's leg. I got the impression that there might be an inroad there for the Orion group and was primarily concerned about anything we could do for protection for these two cats. I may be out of line in asking this, but I feel I do get an asking. Would you please give me information, all the information you can on that subject? I am Ra, the Entity Mind, Body, Spirit, Complex, Gandalf, being harvestable, third density is open to the same type of psychic attack to which you yourselves are vulnerable, therefore, through the mechanism of images and dreams, it is potentially possible for negative concepts to be offered to this mind, body, spirit complex, thus having possible deleterious results of the entity Fairchild, though harvestable through investment, does not have the vulnerability to attack in as great and amount, due to a lack of the mind, a complex activity in the distortion of conscious devotion for a protection of these entities we might indicate two possibilities, firstly, the meditation of putting on the armor of light. Secondly, the repetition of short ritual sentences known to this instrument from the establishment which distorts a spiritual oneness for this instrument. The ritual may be repeated with efficacy from this time until the safe return at convenient intervals.",
